data.description: This house is a rare find, boasting 4 Bedrooms, 3 Bathrooms, Flex room for office, den or crafts and a large second floor recreation/media loft!  This exquisite Lakefront 4/3/2 can be your home with the absolute best location in a gated, 55+ community located in the Horse Capital of the World, Ocala, Florida. Sought after Stone Creek by Dell Webb Community is your perfect paradise for enjoying the 18-hole championship golf course, resort-style pool, clubhouse, state of the art fitness center, spa, community gardens, dog parks, a myriad of game courts and activities with a lifestyle director on staff. Our luxurious Vernon Hill model is a versatile floorplan with open concept modern design which features a kitchen nook with mesmerizing views of the lake, and a large kitchen island/breakfast bar area overlooking the bright, inviting gathering room, making everyday living and entertaining a breeze. Upon entering the grand foyer area the view is captivating as your eyes are drawn to the unrestricted view through the gathering room, screened lanai and on out to the rear yard and the sparkling lake and fountains beyond where you will occasionally see various water birds such as Egrets, silhouetted against the setting sun, resting peacefully at the shoreline. Back inside, you will notice the attention to detail, including the neutral porcelain floor tile, crown molding, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and the very pleasing designer colors throughout. The split floorplan affords privacy for all with two guest bedrooms on the first floor near the front of the house, guest bathroom number two in the hall between them, the primary suite with spa like ensuite bath located at the rear of the house and the fourth bedroom, with bathroom number three, is located up the stairs adjacent to an expansive loft area.  Additionally, on the main level there is a convenient flex room for your home office or art studio as well as a large interior domestic suite with a utility sink, washer and dryer. The 2-car oversized garage includes overhead mounted storage racks that would satisfy any neat-nick's desire to be organized.  Interested in more information? Please reach out for our full color brochure and video tour/photos.
